    <task workspace="3cm" xml:id="PA-trig-tangent-task-1">
      <statement>
        <p>
	            Why is <m>\tan \left( \frac{\pi}{2} \right)</m> not defined?
	            What are three other input values <m>x</m> for which <m>\tan(x)</m> is not defined?
	          </p>
